snippet.title: Mudborne: Frog Management Sim - Launch Trailer | FGS LIVE FROM GDC
snippet.description:
The launch trailer for Mudborne: Frog Management Sim, a casual nature sim where players breed and discover frogs. It's out now on PC, with a free demo available on Steam. A portion of the money made from the game will also be donated towards national and international amphibian, wetlands, and environmental charities. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
